---
title: Turkey Zucchini Bibimbap Bowls with Sweet and Spicy Sauce
description: This Korean rice bowl is packed with veggies, rice and seasoned turkey. Finish it with a Sweet and spicy sauce, then stir all these vibrant ingredients together for a classic Korean experience.

